[normal]&#xa0;[bold]It is incorrect to state that Accenture said it would cost £25 million to start to rebuild the technology from scratch to get to the same position. [bold]&#xa0;
[normal]We
[normal] have spoken to Accenture since Mr Linwood’s written evidence was published and they confirm that during their review for the BBC they did not make any assessment of the cost of rebuilding technology
[normal] equivalent to DMI
[normal].  T
[normal]hey 
[normal]confirmed that they did not say “
[normal]it would cost £25 million to start to rebuild the technology from scratch to get to the same position
[normal]” 
[normal](paragraph 39)
