[normal]&#xa0;
[normal]Accenture did 
[normal]undertake a
[normal] costing for replacing the Archive Database with an off-the-shelf equivalent.
[normal]&#xa0;
[normal] They estimated this cost to be between $6.8-10.4 million (£4.3-6.5 million), which was used to inform the residual value we attributed to this part of the system in the final assessment of the project.
